reviewText:
This seller is so so good. I received the item way ahead of schedule and it came with such a sweet note wishes me and my family the best. Not to mention this is a hard to find item that goes for more everywhere else.

I will most certainly be buying from this seller again. Ichiban!!!

Plus, Okinawa is the most beautiful place in all the world. My mother is Japanese from Okinawa and I recently visited my family in Okinawa and Miyakojima. It was the best time. Thank you for the film, so I can remember it well until I return.
